Does this mean all zodiac believers are going to distance themselves from someone because of a sign? NO! It's just my own experience. And 2 people out of the thousands I've met is a very small percentage. I wanted to bring up the topic to start a discussion and learn more about it. I wanted to hear other perspectives and, truthfully, it's taught me a lot. Apologies if I upset anyone at all. That was not and will never be my intentions.
